="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/behOiHKp268?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Zynga副总裁Sam Cooper补充说：“我们很高兴最终欢迎全球球迷加入Vespaara，并向他们介绍我们令人难以置信的猎人阵容。” “我们游戏中的比赛很容易上手，但很难掌握。我们迫不及待地想看到这一动作，因为球员在竞技场中将其淘汰。祝你好运，银河系正在注视着你！”</p><p> <em>《星球大战》：</em><a href="https://starwarshunters.com/">现在可以</a>免费下载猎人，而Nintendo Switch玩家不需要活跃的在线会员才能玩。</p><p>上个月，据报道， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war">Total War</a></em> Developers <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/creative-assembly">Creative Assembly</a>正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-developer-reportedly-working-on-new-star-wars-game-3757749">制作新的<em>《星球大战》</em>游戏</a>，BIT反应堆还证实了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/ea-still-going-ahead-with-star-wars-strategy-game-despite-cancellation-of-first-person-shooter-3596346">他们的<em>Start Wars</em> Games仍在开发中。</a></p><p>在其他新闻中，看起来<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>可能会来<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fortnite">Fortnite</a>进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/it-looks-like-metallica-are-coming-to-fortnite-for-a-gig-3762698">现场音乐会。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/star-wars-hunters-launches-on-nintendo-switch-and-mobile-3762750">“星球大战：猎人”在Nintendo Switch上发布，Mobile</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
